              h3.description__title Tear resistant paper
              p.description__text Next generation paper which you won't be able to tear. Because of the quality, the notebook is durable and stays as new for a long time.
          video(src="./img/video-1.webm" loop autoplay type="video/webm" class="carousel__video")
